The '''Australia and New Zealand Unitarian Universalist Association ''' or '''ANZUUA''' is a [[Unitarian Universalism|Unitarian Universalist]] organisation which serves as the organising body for [[Unitarianism|Unitarian]] and [[Universalist]] congregations in [[Australia]] and [[New Zealand]]. ANZUUA was established in 1974 as the Australia and New Zealand Unitarian Association.
