'''Satanachia''' is described in the ''[[Grand Grimoire]]'' as a commander-in-chief of Satan's army, who controls either forty-five or fifty-four legions of demons, including [[Pruflas]], [[Aamon]], [[Barbatos]], and [[Astaroth]].  According to the ''Grand Grimoire'', he has the power to subjugate all women and girls, and to do with them whatever he wishes.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://sacred-texts.com/grim/bcm/bcm51.htm |title=Book of Ceremonial Magic: Chapter III: Concerning the Descending Hierarchy: Section 1: The Names and Offices of Evil Spirits |publisher=Sacred-texts.com |accessdate=2017-04-13}}</ref>

