'''Sikh Chola''' is traditional dress worn by Sikhs. It is a martial attire which gives freedom of movement to a Sikh warrior.<ref>[http://www.sikhstuff.com Sikh Chola Images]</ref><ref>[http://sikhism.about.com/od/glossary/g/Chhollaa.htm Chola Definition by About.com]</ref> Sikh Chola is also unisex attire, and may also be decorated with heavy [[embroidery]] all over it or on the chest.

